SYNOPSIS
========
   int valid_trace(string what, int|string arg)

DESCRIPTION
===========
   Check if the interactive user is allowed to use tracing.

   The argument what(M) denotes the action for which permission is to be 
   checked, arg(M) is the argument given to trace(E).

   +---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | what(M)       | notes                                                                            |
   +===============+==================================================================================+
   | "trace"       | Is the user allowed to use tracing? arg(M) is the tracelevel argument  given.    |
   +---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | "traceprefix" | Is the user allowed to set a traceprefix? arg(M) is the prefix given.            |
   +---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

SEE ALSO
========
   trace(E), >>:concept:`memory`<<
